# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore — public archival release of the PQ-ID prototype.
#
# This release repository differs from the development .gitignore in one
# deliberate way: it COMMITS the pinned, reproducible artifacts that let a
# reviewer verify proofs, gas, and tests on any platform WITHOUT first running
# the full native toolchain — namely the trusted-setup outputs
# (setup/out/*.zkey, *.json, *.sol), the circuit build products
# (circuits/build/, except the 38 MB research r1cs), and the measured
# results (results/*.json). Every committed artifact's SHA-256 is pinned in
# setup/pins.json and re-verified by the determinism test, so the committed
# copies stay byte-identical to a fresh `make setup`.
#
# Still ignored: dependencies, caches, secrets, platform-specific binaries,
# the downloadable powers-of-tau, and regenerated intermediates/logs.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Dependencies / build state
node_modules/
dist/
*.tsbuildinfo

# Runtime keys — never committed
fixtures/keys/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/

# Editor / OS
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Powers-of-tau (powersOfTau28_hez_final_15.ptau, ~38 MB, SHA-256-pinned in
# setup/pins.json) IS committed here for long-term archival robustness, so the
# trusted setup and the determinism pin-check work without depending on an
# external download URL that may rot. `setup/download_ptau.ts` finds the
# existing file and only re-verifies its pin. Any OTHER ptau is ignored.
setup/ptau/*
!setup/ptau/powersOfTau28_hez_final_15.ptau

# Trusted-setup intermediate (only the finalized zkey is committed)
setup/out/credential_auth_0000.zkey

# Research circuit r1cs: ~38 MB, regenerated by setup/research_sha3_report.ts.
# Only its tiny JSON summary (sha3_research_info.json) is committed.
circuits/build/research/sha3_incircuit.r1cs

# Platform-specific tool binaries (see tools/README.md for how to obtain the
# pinned circom 2.2.3 and Foundry builds). Not committed.
tools/circom.exe
tools/foundry/

# Packaging staging + transient benchmark logs
package_supplementary/
pqid-prototype-supplementary.zip
results/_bench_*.log
